    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Duelist</defName>
        <label>Duelist</label>
        <treeClass>Duelist</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Masters of the blade who turn defense into devastation. Five constellations radiate from the duelist's core — each honing a different edge of their relentless technique. Dodge incoming strikes to charge Counter Strike, then unleash every stored charge in a single devastating blow.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>CounterStrike</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Counter Strike</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>Every melee attack that misses the Duelist (dodge) stores a counter charge. The next outgoing melee hit consumes ALL charges for bonus melee damage. Counter Strike scales along the Centerpoint Path. Tier 1 (Parry): max 3 charges, +7% melee damage each (max +21%). Tier 2 (Riposte): max 5 charges, +8% each (max +40%). Tier 3 (Blade Dance): max 7 charges, +9% each (max +63%). Tier 4 (Perfect Counter): max 10 charges, +10% each (max +100%). Turn their mistakes into your victory.</classGimmickDescription>

